<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<title>Mandarin Minds Lesson Alert</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<style type="text/css" media="screen">
	body{
		width: 700px;
	}
	.header{
		background: #2c3e50;
		width: 100%;
		height: 75px;
		border-radius: 10px;
	}
	
	.logo{
		padding-left: 15px;
		vertical-align: middle;
	}
	
	.body-wrap{
		width: 100%;
		border: #e5eaee solid 2px;
		border-radius: 10px;
		margin-top:	10px;
		padding: 5px;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-family: "proxima-nova",sans-serif;
		font-style: normal;
		font-weight: 100;
	}
	
	.in-line-img{
		height: 140px;
		width: 650px;
		display: block;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		border-radius: 10px;	
	}
	
	h1 {
		color: #93192C;
		font-size: 22px;
	}
</style>
</head>
<body style="width: 700px;">
<!-- HEADER -->
<table class="header" style="background: #2c3e50;width: 100%;height: 50px;border-radius: 10px;">
	<td><img class="logo" alt="Logo" src='https://www.mandarinminds.com/images/logo.png' style="padding-left: 15px;vertical-align: middle;"></td>	
</table>
<!-- /HEADER -->


<!-- BODY -->
<table class="body-wrap" style="width: 100%;border: #e5eaee solid 2px;border-radius: 10px;margin-top: 10px;padding: 5px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &quot;proxima-nova&quot;,sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-weight: 100;">
	<tr>
		<td>						
			<h1 style="color: #93192C;font-size: 22px;">Your Lesson Alert for <%= Time.now.in_time_zone("Perth").strftime("#{Time.now.in_time_zone("Perth").day.ordinalize} %b %Y")%></h1>
			
			<p>Good morning. The following is the list of Mandarin Minds students who have not purchased lessons from us.</p>

			<% timezone_offset = 8 %>
			<table>
				<tr><td><b>Student</b></td><td><b>Email</b></td><td><b>Signup Date</b></td><td><b>Lessons Left</b></td></tr>
				<% @students.each do |s| %>
				<tr>
					<td><%= "#{s.firstname} #{s.lastname}" %></td>
					<td><%= s.email %></td>
					<td><%= s.created_at.strftime('%F') %></td>
					<td><%= s.lesson_count %></td>
					
				</tr>
				<% end %>
			</table>
			<ul>
				
			</ul>
			Times are given in UTC +8

																	

		</td></tr>
		
					
		
<!-- /BODY -->


<!-- /FOOTER -->
</table></body>
</html>